text: Yovcho Khristov (born 25 February 1913, date of death unknown) was a Bulgarian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Bulgarian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Bulgaria Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
